        <tr valign=top> 
          <td width=30><img height=8 alt="" 
      src="../images/common/1ptrans.gif" width=30 border=0></td>
          <td width=590><b>How do I apply for Basic Membership?</b> 
            <ul>
              <li>Singaporeans may apply for library membership using the online 
                ' Apply for Membership form' 
              <li>Those who opt to use their NRIC as their membership card, must 
                visit the selected branch library to activate it. 
              <li>Permanent residents and foreigners will not be able to use this 
                online form. They will have to apply personally at a branch library. 
              </li>
            </ul>
            <b>Note the following items and fees:</b> 
            <table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=4 width=550 border=1>
              <tbody> 
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td width=50><b>Status</b></td>
                <td width=50><br>
                </td>
                <td width=150><b>Items To Bring</b></td>
                <td width=300><b>Fees</b></td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Singaporean</td>
                <td>15 years &amp; above</td>
                <td>NRIC</td>
                <td>- No fee for using NRIC as membership card<br>
                  OR<br>
                  $5.00 if need membership card</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td><br>
                </td>
                <td>Child</td>
                <td>i) Birth certificate<br>
                  ii) Parent's NRIC</td>
                <td>- Free membership card</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Permanent<br>
                  Resident</td>
                <td>15 years &amp; above</td>
                <td>i) Passport<br>
                  ii) Re-entry permit or blue I/C </td>
                <td>- No fee for using blue NRIC as membership card<br>
                  OR<br>
                  - $5.00 if need membership card<br>
                  - $10.30 registration fee</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td><br>
                </td>
                <td>Child</td>
                <td>i) Birth certificate or passport<br>
                  ii) Parent's NRIC</td>
                <td>- Free membership card<br>
                  - $10.30 registration fee</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Non-citizen</td>
                <td>Adult</td>
                <td>i) Passport<br>
                  ii) Employment pass or Dependent pass</td>
                <td>i) $10.30 registration fee<br>
                  ii) $10.30 annual subscription (Includes membership card fee)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td><br>
                </td>
                <td>Child</td>
                <td>i) Child's Passport<br>
                  ii) Parent's Passport<br>
                  iii) Student pass or Dependent pass</td>
                <td>i) $10.30 registration fee<br>
                  ii) $10.30 annual subscription (Includes membership card fee)</td>
              </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <p><b>Basic Membership Privileges</b> 
            <p> 
            <table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=4 width=550 border=0>
              <tbody> 
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Loan Quota</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>You can use either your NRIC or membership card to borrow 
                  a maximum of 4 books or magazines.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr> 
                <td>Loan Period</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>21 days</td>
              </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
