      <table cellspacing=5 cellpadding=5 width=620 border=0>
        <tbody> 
        <tr valign=top> 
          <td width=30><img height=8 alt="" 
      src="../images/common/1ptrans.gif" width=30 border=0></td>
          <td width=590><b>How do I apply for Premium Membership?</b> 
            <p>You have to be a library member before you can apply for the Premium 
              Service. Note that Video-Lending members are automatically converted 
              to Premium Service members. 
            <p> 
            <table cellspacing=5 cellpadding=5 width=550>
              <tbody> 
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Registration</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>Register as a Premium Service member at the Customer Services 
                  Counter of any community or regional library with your NRIC 
                  or library membership card.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Annual Subscription Fee</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>$20.60 (including 3% GST). This fee is non-refundable.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Privileges</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>Premium Service members can borrow up to eight items (books, 
                  magazines, videos or CD-ROMs).</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Loan Quota</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>Premium Service members can use either their NRIC or membership 
                  card to borrow an additional four items on top of the four books 
                  or magazines. These items can be books, magazines, videos or 
                  CD-ROMs.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Loan Period</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>21 days for books and magazines. Seven days for videos and 
                  CD-ROMs.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Collection</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>Audio-Visual Lending items can only be collected from the 
                  Libraries, where they are located, and cannot be routed to another 
                  library for pick-up.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr valign=top> 
                <td>Policy</td>
                <td>:</td>
                <td>The videos and CD-ROMs borrowed from the library are strictly 
                  for private viewing. Duplication, circulation and renting out 
                  of the tapes and CD-ROMs are not allowed.</td>
              </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
